<br>
I've had occasions in places with bad pathing where a roamer in a different part of the dungeon thought it could swing at me, and as a result, aggroed my pet.  When I got close to the area with said stupid mob my pet would run off and attack it, since my pet thought it attacked me first.<br>
<br>
